ristic#Area_under_the_curve" title=3D"Receiver operating characteristic">AU=
C</a>):<sup id=3D"cite_ref-8" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wik=
ipedia.org/wiki/Mann%E2%80%93Whitney_U_test#cite_note-8"><span class=3D"cit=
e-bracket">[</span>8<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
