<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Properties">Properties</h2>=
<span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</sp=
an><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DMann%E2%80%93Whi=
tney_U_test&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D5" title=3D"Edit section: Prope=
rties"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span>=
</span></div>
<p>The maximum value of <i>U</i> is the product of the sample sizes for the=
 two samples (i.e.: <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline=
"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"disp=
lay: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{=
\displaystyle U_{i}=3Dn_{1}n_{2}}">
