-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -2.171ex; width:14.213ex; height:5.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle z=
=3D{\frac {U-m_{U}}{\sigma _{U}}},\,}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>where <i>m</i><sub><i>U</i></sub> and <i>=CF=83</i><sub><i>U</i></sub> a=
