 normal deviate whose significance can be checked in tables of the normal d=
istribution. <i>m</i><sub><i>U</i></sub> and <i>=CF=83</i><sub><i>U</i></su=
b> are given by
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
