p?title=3DMann%E2%80%93Whitney_U_test&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D17" t=
itle=3D"Edit section: Different distributions"><span>edit</span></a><span c=
lass=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The Mann=E2=80=93Whitney <i>U</i> test is not valid for testing the null=
 hypothesis <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span =
